I need to make a good impression at work.

594
00:32:28,100 --> 00:32:29,500
(LAUGHING)

595
00:32:29,600 --> 00:32:30,800
What?

596
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,400
Your plans. That's just...

597
00:32:35,500 --> 00:32:36,900
What are you talking...

598
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:39,500
