601
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:48,600
People want to change the world,
don't know how to begin.

602
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:53,900
You want to know
how to change the world, son?

603
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:57,800
One act of random kindness at a time.

604
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:07,900
Build the ark.

605
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:11,000
I'll tell you what. You build it, I'll fill it.

606
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:16,500
And if anybody asks,
tell them a flood's coming.

607
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:21,100
Oh, and you might need this.

608
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:28,900
Well, okay. Okay, so what do I do?
I grab the wood and...

609
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:30,500
Well, okay.

610
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:33,900
