611
00:33:35,500 --> 00:33:37,000
Do you see him?

612
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:39,600
I don't see him.

613
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:44,100
"Building an Ark the Old-Fashioned Way."

614
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:49,700
"God is the creator of
the Heavens and the Earth.

615
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:54,700
"He lives in all things and has over
