Okay. Okay.

622
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,800
Yeah.

623
00:35:10,900 --> 00:35:13,900
There we go. Okay.

624
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,800
(EXCLAIMS)

625
00:35:20,900 --> 00:35:24,400
Come on. I mean, a beard?
