626
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:27,300
Gross!

627
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:29,600
JOAN: Packing, so it would really help me
out if you would...

628
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,700
Good morning.

629
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,900
Hey, hey, hey, good morning.

630
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:32,900
(CHUCKLING)

631
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,300
Wow.

632
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:36,900
What's with the scruffle, mountain man?

633
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:42,300
Oh, well, you know, I figured it was
a weekend, and I thought...

634
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:43,500
JOAN: What?

635
00:35:43,600 --> 00:35:44,600
(MUTTERING)

636
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:45,900
(BOTH GIGGLING)

637
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:49,300
Honey, did I miss something?
