714
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:14,400
"Well, I'm building an ark."

715
00:39:15,700 --> 00:39:16,800
(GROANING)

716
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:20,200
I got a boo-boo! I got a boo-boo!
