736
00:40:30,600 --> 00:40:32,100
Okay. All right.

737
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:35,500
Okay, that's great. It's longer.

738
00:40:35,500 --> 00:40:38,400
Oh, my God. It is you.

739
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:41,100
